        <trans-unit id="166" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Job types</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="167" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Use job types to classify similar jobs into categories.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="168" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Job types, just like job functions, can be assigned to jobs and used to set up and implement eligibility rules for compensation plans.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="169" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Some examples of job types are included in the following list:</source>
